# DaCapo Canonical Reference

## 1. Core Principles

- Firestore is the single source of truth.
- All application data lives under `/apps/{appId}`.
- Frontend location NEVER determines data ownership.
- Users do not own apps. Apps own users.
- Legacy structures are forbidden.

--------------------------------------------------

## 2. App Topology (Canonical)

- `dacapotools.nl` is the central launcher / portal.
- Each tool is a standalone app hosted on its own subdomain:
  - `{appId}.dacapotools.nl`
- Subdomain name MUST equal `appId`.

Examples:
- nieuwsbrief.dacapotools.nl → `appId = nieuwsbrief`
- pacogenerator.dacapotools.nl → `appId = pacogenerator`
- nablijfapp.dacapotools.nl → `appId = nablijfapp`

--------------------------------------------------

